{"id":"zebulonite","term":"Zebulonite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The designation of Elon, the judge who belonged to the tribe of Zebulun (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 12:11\">Judg. 12:11</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 12:12\">12</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Judges 12:11","Judges 12:12"]}